XHatSwitch 1.0
by Chris Strosser

DESCRIPTION
===========
Supplements the four native X-Plane hat switch commands to 
allow full use of eight-way hat switches.

INSTALLATION
============
Copy the XHatSwitch folder into your X-Plane plugins folder.

REQUIREMENTS
============
Windows

(if someone is willing to compile Linux and Mac versions, I would be happy to include them)